2738. FROM ENNIO FILONARDI.

Leipzig MS. Lucerne. EE. 181. 13 November 1532.

[An original letter. written by a secretary, signed by Filonardi, who also writes the first five words and makes one correction. There is a copy of this letter, made by Hottinger‘s secretary at Zuricli, MS. F. 52. 120.]
